! XKeysymDB - vendor virtual keysym definitions (Motif/OSF).
!
! Standard MIT-licensed X11 keysym data, recreated for retro5 / WordPerfect 8.
! WP's bundled 1998 libX11 resolves Motif virtual keysyms (osfXXX) used by its
! text-field translation tables through this file. Modern X no longer ships it
! (it was dropped from x11-common), so on a current system XStringToKeysym()
! cannot resolve "osfDelete"/"osfLeft"/... -> the entry-field translations for
! Delete, BackSpace and the arrow keys never install and those keys fall through
! to self-insert (garbage glyphs). Point WP's libX11 at this file with
! XKEYSYMDB=<path> to restore normal editing in dialog text fields.
!
